<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="36" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="19.[136,1452,158,437]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,486,230,256]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Distribution and ecology</emphasis>
:—It is restricted to the Northeast of 
<collectingCountry box="[907,975,230,256]" name="Brazil" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(AL, BA, CE, MA, PB, PE, PI, RN, SE), associated with the phytogeographic domain of the Caatinga (Queiroz 2009; BFG 2018).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[136,1452,158,437]" box="[189,712,302,329]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,351,302,328]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Phenology:—</emphasis>
Registered with flowers in May.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="36" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="19.[136,1452,158,437]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,484,338,364]" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Taxonomic discussion:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. S. Irwin &amp; Barneby" authorityYear="1982" box="[483,634,339,365]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Senna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="19" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rizzinii">
<emphasis box="[483,634,339,365]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Senna rizzinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be recognized, mainly, by the shrubby habit, inermous branches, lateral stipules, terminal raceme, zygomorphic flowers with yellow corolla and bacoid fruits. It resembles 
<taxonomicName box="[1232,1452,374,401]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Senna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="19" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macranthera">
<emphasis box="[1232,1452,374,401]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">Senna macranthera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
morphologically, but can be distinguished by the ovate bracts in 
<emphasis box="[858,1001,411,437]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. S. Irwin &amp; Barneby" authorityYear="1982" box="[858,964,411,437]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Senna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="19" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rizzinii">S. rizzinii</taxonomicName>
vs.
</emphasis>
linear bracts in 
<taxonomicName box="[1182,1355,410,437]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Senna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="19" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macranthera">
<emphasis box="[1182,1355,410,437]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="36">S. macranthera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
